1
00:00:00,290 --> 00:00:01,920
Alright, here we go.

2
00:00:02,250 --> 00:00:04,380
Um, does it have to be today?

3
00:00:04,380 --> 00:00:07,880
Looking good.
Let me fix my hair.

4
00:00:08,590 --> 00:00:10,550
Oh, no, you don't have to... Sorry.

5
00:00:10,550 --> 00:00:12,510
Around here, right?
What do you think?

6
00:00:12,510 --> 00:00:15,100
Maybe somewhere like here...
I think this looks better.

7
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:20,560
(What's going on?
Why are they smiling so much?)

8
00:00:20,560 --> 00:00:22,190
(Okay.)

9
00:00:22,190 --> 00:00:23,520
That's not a good idea.

10
00:00:23,520 --> 00:00:25,530
He really is good-looking.

11
00:00:25,530 --> 00:00:26,900
Thank you for your hard work.

12
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:30,610
Thank you so much for today.

13
00:00:30,610 --> 00:00:32,280
Um, what are you guys doing?

14
00:00:32,280 --> 00:00:33,660
Sorry if we disturbed you.

15
00:00:33,660 --> 00:00:35,450
Are you going to remove your makeup?

16
00:00:35,450 --> 00:00:37,360
No, that's not what I meant.

17
00:00:37,830 --> 00:00:39,540
You just looked like you were having so much fun.

18
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:45,800
If you don't mind,
would you let me take the photo?

19
00:00:46,130 --> 00:00:48,470
Oh, no, we couldn't possibly
have you do that...

20
00:00:48,470 --> 00:00:50,880
They went to college together.

21
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:52,930
So they go way back?!

22
00:00:52,930 --> 00:00:55,560
Ah, yes, we're friends.

23
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:58,020
You won't be as nervous if a friend takes it, right?

24
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:03,650
Oh, well... would you mind taking a few shots?
